notes: *Table does not include contributions to parish precepts, fire brigade, social care and any other contributions payable in addition to Council Tax.
Note: The non-metropolitan county of Northamptonshire, together with its seven districts, has been dissolved and two new unitary authorities have been created (as of 1 April 2021):
North Northamptonshire: comprised of Corby, East Northamptonshire, Kettering and Wellingborough
West Northamptonshire: comprised of Daventry, Northampton and South Northamptonshire
*Table does not include contributions to parish council precepts, fire brigade, social care and any other contributions payable in addition to Council Tax.
Note: Scotland has frozen all rates for 2021-22.
